Aloha President Kouchi, Speaker Nakamura, and Members of the Legislature:
This is to inform you that on May 27, 2026, the following bill was signed into law:
H.B. NO. 2592, H.D. 2, S.D. 2, RELATING TO THE MAUNA KEA STEWARDSHIP
C.D. 1 AND OVERSIGHT AUTHORITY.
